Excuse me.

00:10.010 --> 00:12.240
I know we haven't been
formally introduced...

00:12.412 --> 00:15.942
...but I was wondering.
when you get off from work...

00:16.116 --> 00:18.176
...if you haven't made
any dinner p|ans...?

