in a Nobel Peace Prize. Dan?

00:56.654 --> 00:58.754
Career advancement.

00:59.357 --> 01:02.787
Of course.
I lost my head there for a second.

01:04.194 --> 01:07.095
Excuse me. I'm afraid I'm a little lost.

01:07.265 --> 01:09.095
I was wondering if you could direct me.

01:09.267 --> 01:13.427
Certainly. first left. take the corridor.
and then follow the yellow brick road.

01:19.878 --> 01:22.108
I crack myself up.

01:27.652 --> 01:29.782
Who are you?

01:29.954 --> 01:33.624
Dan Fielding. Can you say that?

01:38.830 --> 01:43.030
I'm Vincent Daniels. your new boss.

01:46.137 --> 01:48.727
Can you say that?

01:50.874 --> 01:54.374
I'll expect you in my office immediately.

02:00.317 --> 02:03.877
Heigh-ho. heigh-ho...

02:04.054 --> 02:06.924
