-Oh. thank you. sir.

05:11.798 --> 05:14.318
-Defense requests a psychiatric--
-Whoa. Miss Sullivan.

05:14.501 --> 05:18.131
I would like to hear the particulars
of this case before we pass judgment.

05:18.305 --> 05:21.425
