Mr. Fielding.

06:01.877 --> 06:05.967
Excuse me.
Vinnie the Pooh wants to see me.

06:07.081 --> 06:08.411
WOMEN:
Oooh....

06:08.582 --> 06:12.142
Hey! You can forget
those Christmas cards.

06:13.487 --> 06:15.147
-What?
-Mr. Fielding.

06:15.321 --> 06:19.091
Ethics aside. I found your comments
to the defendant disgusting...

06:19.259 --> 06:21.189
...and totally unacceptable.

06:22.461 --> 06:24.331
So. what's your point?

06:24.897 --> 06:28.587
