how I want things handled in this court.

06:28.766 --> 06:31.996
-I have been doing this job for eight years--
-Sit!

06:35.006 --> 06:40.496
Look. listen and learn.

06:42.814 --> 06:45.284
I hated you in E.T.

06:50.655 --> 06:54.015
