I would like to cite a relevant precedent.

06:54.192 --> 06:57.092
Namely. Green v. Wisconsin,
1962. in which--

06:57.261 --> 07:00.201
You mean Greenberg v. Wisconsin.

07:00.364 --> 07:02.304
Greenberg. right.

07:02.466 --> 07:05.796
-As I was saying--
-And it was 1972.

07:06.304 --> 07:08.244
-What did I say?
-'62.

07:09.606 --> 07:12.096
Hey. you got the state part right.

07:13.276 --> 07:14.896
How clever of me.

07:15.078 --> 07:18.608
With all due respect
to counsel for the defense...

07:18.782 --> 07:23.852
...the Greenberg decision
was overturned by the Supreme Court.

07:25.956 --> 07:29.356
It was a 6-to-2 vote
with one abstention...

07:29.525 --> 07:33.455
...on August 17th. 1977.

07:36.098 --> 07:41.968
-I believe it was a Thursday.
-It was a Tuesday.

07:44.640 --> 07:46.570
I'm just kidding.

07:48.177 --> 07:49.197
I know.

07:53.249 --> 07:54.579
Defense have anything to add?

07:55.217 --> 07:59.477
I respectfully decline. Your Honor.
on the grounds that it may incriminate me.

07:59.655 --> 08:00.845
Mr. Fielding?

08:01.423 --> 08:06.333
Her turn-ons are sunshine. smiles
and Bert Convy movies.

08:07.763 --> 08:11.533
Dan. Yo. Do you concur with Mr. Daniels?

08:12.234 --> 08:17.104
Well. if the pointy little shoe
with the bell on the toe fits....

08:19.074 --> 08:23.244
Okay. I don't see any reason we can't
continue this case till the next session.

08:23.412 --> 08:24.442
We will take a short--

08:25.447 --> 08:28.307
I mean. a little-- I mean....

08:28.484 --> 08:32.554
-"Short" is fine.
-"Short" it is. Short recess.

08:33.489 --> 08:37.589
Fielding. I've got a problem
with your attitude.

08:38.660 --> 08:40.691
Did you say "attitude"...

08:41.596 --> 08:44.496
...or "altitude"?

08:46.301 --> 08:49.861
Your behavior is bordering
on insubordination.

08:50.038 --> 08:52.198
-Now. you listen to me--
-No. you listen to me.

08:52.706 --> 08:55.506
I'm giving you one week
to clean up your act.

08:55.676 --> 08:57.236
Is that understood?

08:59.313 --> 09:01.253
Understood?

09:02.349 --> 09:04.719
-Yes.
-Yes. what?

09:04.885 --> 09:06.375
Yes. you little ba--

09:08.755 --> 09:10.475
Barrister.

09:11.823 --> 09:13.623
Fielding.

09:16.728 --> 09:19.158
I don't think we see eye-to-eye.

09:19.331 --> 09:24.531
You wanna see eye-to-eye?
You want to see eye-to-eye?

