20:58.660 --> 21:02.060
Well. it's kind of private.

21:06.300 --> 21:09.290
That roast should be done by now.

21:12.940 --> 21:16.670
-Florence. it's not going to work.
-It's not?

21:16.844 --> 21:20.114
Don't get me wrong.
it's not that I don't find you attractive...

21:20.280 --> 21:22.410
...it's just. well...

21:22.583 --> 21:27.613
...I'm used to a certain pace
when it comes to relationships.

21:27.788 --> 21:28.848
Like?

21:29.023 --> 21:32.933
Like you're a Corvette
and I'm a milk truck.

21:33.560 --> 21:34.690
Oh.

21:35.896 --> 21:38.016
I'm sorry. really I am.

21:38.198 --> 21:42.468
Well. I guess if that's the way you feel.

21:42.636 --> 21:43.826
It is.

21:44.004 --> 21:46.344
And listen. who knows?

21:46.507 --> 21:48.437
In a few years...

21:48.609 --> 21:53.209
...after you'll have gotten all of this
out of your system....

21:55.014 --> 21:56.314
Goodbye. Florence.

21:58.016 --> 21:59.576
Goodbye. Bernie.

22:12.931 --> 22:15.831
Ee-vah!

